name: OMEGA
description: OMEGA is more than a meme coin—it’s a movement fueled by energy and loyalty. The culture, real-life experiences, and brand are all powered by the dedicated fellowship of its community, with generous rewards for those who join. OMEGA is the demon you worship, a mischievous presence whispering in your ear, urging you toward thrilling pursuits. Those who follow OMEGA are rewarded, for the true ALPHA has always been OMEGA.
